    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor Compact Portable Bore Cord Pistol Gun Cleaning Rope Tool uses a three-pass cleaning system to clean out debris from the barrel of your gun, ensuring the continued safe firing and functionality of your gun(s). Employing a leader rope, followed by a cleaning rope and bronze bristle, the bore cord cleaning rope tool is a fast and efficient way to clean your gun when you’re in the field or at the range away from your regular cleaning supplies and resources. Caliber compatibility listed below: .22CAL Pistol Rope Cleaning compatible with.22 and 5.56MM caliber pistols</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Compact Rope Gun Cleaning Tool (4 Caliber Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor Compact Portable Bore Cord Pistol Gun Cleaning Rope Tool uses a three-pass cleaning system to clean out debris from the barrel of your gun, ensuring the continued safe firing and functionality of your gun(s). Employing a leader rope, followed by a cleaning rope and bronze bristle, the bore cord cleaning rope tool is a fast and efficient way to clean your gun when you’re in the field or at the range away from your regular cleaning supplies and resources.</p>\n  <p>Caliber compatibility listed below: .22CAL Pistol Rope Cleaning compatible with.22 and 5.56MM caliber pistols</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>QUICK AND EASY GUN CLEANING TOOL:</strong> The ASR Outdoor Compact Portable Bore Cord Pistol Gun Cleaning Rope Tool uses a three-pass cleaning system to clean out debris from the barrel of your gun, ensuring the continued safe firing and functionality of your gun(s); optimal when used with gun cleaning solutions, solvents or oils; no assembly required</li>\n    <li><strong>COMPACT AND TRAVEL FRIENDLY:</strong> Folding up to fit in the palm of your hand, the gun rope cleaner will easily fit in any backpack, gun range bag or other; use the leader rope at the beginning of the tool to wrap around the cleaning rope and secure; this is a great tool to include with your camping, hunting or general outdoor equipment or survival gear as well</li>\n    <li><strong>REUSEABLE AND WASHABLE:</strong> The nylon bore cleaning rope absorbs well, is machine or hand washable and reusable hundreds of times over to help maintain a consistently clean gun barrel or gun chamber; safe to use with fun cleaning solvents</li>\n    <li><strong>AVAILABLE STYLES:</strong> .22CAL Pistol Rope Cleaning compatible with.22 and 5.56MM caliber pistols; .44CAL Pistol Rope Cleaner compatible with 44,.45,.70, .416,.458 and .460 caliber pistols; 9MM CAL Pistol Rope Cleaner compatible with .357, .380,.38 and 9MM caliber pistols; .308CAL Pistol Rope Cleaner compatible with .308,.30-35,30-06, .300,.303 and 7.62MM caliber pistols</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Open Length Dimensions: 58 inches; Folded Length Dimensions: 4 inches; Color: Black Multi; Material: Nylon/Polyester</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/44071/gun_rope_var.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Outdoor Compact Portable Bore Cord Pistol Gun Cleaning Rope Tool uses a three-pass cleaning system to clean out debris from the barrel of your\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>.44CAL Pistol Rope Cleaner compatible with 44,.45,.70, .416,.458 and .460 caliber pistols</p>\n  <p>.9MM CAL Pistol Rope Cleaner compatible with .357, .380,.38 and 9MM caliber pistols</p>\n  <p>.308CAL Pistol Rope Cleaner compatible with .308,.30-35,30-06, .300,.303 and 7.62MM caliber pistols</p>\n  <p>Folding up to fit in the palm of your hand, the gun rope cleaner will easily fit in any backpack, gun range bag or other; use the leader rope at the beginning of the tool to wrap around the cleaning rope and secure; this is a great tool to include with your camping, hunting or general outdoor equipment or survival gear as well as it can come in hand for other tasks.</p>\n  <p>Lastly, the nylon bore cleaning rope absorbs well, is machine or hand washable and reusable hundreds of times over to help maintain a consistently clean gun barrel or gun chamber; safe to use with fun cleaning solvents, solutions or oils.</p>\n  <p>NOTE: ALWAYS remove the clip and clear the chamber before cleaning; No assembly/disassembly is required</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ASR Outdoor Compact Portable Bore Cord Pistol Gun Cleaning Rope Tool uses a three-pass cleaning system to clean out debris from the barrel of your gun, ensuring the continued safe firing and functionality of your gun(s). Employing a leader rope, followed by a cleaning rope and bronze bristle, the bore cord cleaning rope tool is a fast and efficient way to clean your gun when you’re in the field or at the range away from your regular cleaning supplies and resources. Caliber compatibility listed below: .22CAL Pistol Rope Cleaning compatible with.22 and 5.56MM caliber pistols.",
